      "content": "but it doesn't feel like an evolution. it just feels like... a mistake. like i'm just occupying space that should have been empty. there's no \"new person\" here, just the leftovers of someone who actually mattered. it's hard to see the point in carrying around all this weight when the heart of it is already gone.",
